des:
My Advice Mechanic helps users figure out what's causing common car problems, like noise, smoke and starting engine.

All you need is to say "Alexa, ask My Advice Mechanic". Alexa will ask you a few simple Yes or No questions. At the end, Alexa will tell you the most likely cause of your car problem.
